        "type": "paragraph",
        "id": "e6699ae6-8b6e-4b2e-afb4-f6cc8fff22a1",
        "text": "When the paper was written, there were three manual, paper-based IBIS-type systems in use—two in government agencies and one in a university."
      },
      "after": "8d7f276d-16ac-4d77-8e94-e912b7d4132b",
      "id": "e6699ae6-8b6e-4b2e-afb4-f6cc8fff22a1",
